The paper deals with codes and their properties, specifically weak isometries. This falls under the category of information theory (cs.IT) and discrete mathematics (cs.DM). The paper also involves graph theory, which is a subfield of computer science (cs.CC). Additionally, the paper discusses codes of a certain length, which could fall under the category of signal processing (cs.SI) or data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
